

	 
      i finally found that moment.  that moment in life that i wish i could go back and do again.  actually there is three of them.  but they would all change the same outcome.  why didn't i open my mouth on the phone?  why didn't i say something when he got there?  why didn't i speak up after the incident?  it was me, the whole time, not him.  i can see the look in his eyes that meant everything changed.  but i can not go back, i can not do it again.  all that i can do is wait for a similar moment and try to do things right this time and hope that is tips the scales of karmic energy back to neutral....
     
    
